data.description: What a find!  This 3-Bedroom home is located near two Interstate Highways and convenient to shopping and dining areas. It’s situated in Lexington/Richland School District 5. The roof was replaced in 2020, hot water heater in 2020, dishwasher and range hood in 2023. Appliances (refrigerator, range, microwave, dishwasher) convey with acceptable offer.  It’s a great time to become a homeowner; This home is waiting for you!
